        <span class="w3-large"><b>Listado caniones para el pary!!</b> </span><br>
        <span>Queremos que nos ayudes a ambientar nuestra fiesta!!
          Por eso puede agregar tu cancion favorita y la pondemos en el repertorio musical
          Da click aqui para agregar tu cancion</span><br>
          <%= link_to '<button class=" w3-center w3-button  w3-green w3-border w3-round" type="button">Agergar cancion</button>'.html_safe, new_article_path %>


        </li>
        <li class="w3-padding-16">
          <img src="http://www.brandemia.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/2rgyj4m.jpg" alt="Image" class="w3-left w3-margin-right" style="width:50px">
          <span class="w3-large"> <b>Lista de reproduccion Spotify</b></span><br>
          <span>Quieres escuchar nuesto play list!! da click aqui para ponerte al dia</span><br>
          <iframe class="w3-center"src="https://embed.spotify.com/?uri=spotify%3Auser%3Aga3o%3Aplaylist%3A3YBta2heAai5qP62mzoM9L" width="300" height="380" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true"></iframe>      </li>


        </ul>
      </div>
      <hr>
  <!-- Posts -->
  <div class="w3-card-2 w3-margin">
    <div class="w3-container w3-padding">
      <h4>Informacion importante</h4>
    </div>
    <ul class="w3-ul w3-hoverable w3-white">
      <li class="w3-padding-16">
        <img src="http://diocesisdemexicali.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/PARROQUIA_LA_SAGRADA_FAMILIA04-150x150.jpg" alt="Image" class="w3-left w3-margin-right" style="width:50px">
        <span class="w3-large">Ceremonia Religiosa</span><br>
        <span>Misa: Parroquia de la Sagrada Familia</span>
        <span> Av. 56 y Libertador- Col. Hidalgo sur- 21389 Mexicali, B.C.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="w3-padding-16">
        <img src="http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah93/ingraulreyes/civil_zpsrwm9buuo.png" alt="Image" class="w3-left w3-margin-right" style="width:50px">
        <span class="w3-large">Boda civil </span><br>
        <span>Jardin Versalles </span>
        <span>Avenida República de Uruguay 51, Cuauhtémoc Sur, 21200 </span>
        <span>7:00 PM</span>
      </li>
      <li class="w3-padding-16">
        <img src="http://i1378.photobucket.com/albums/ah93/ingraulreyes/recepcion_zpsy9x0blqw.png" alt="Image" class="w3-left w3-margin-right" style="width:50px">
        <span class="w3-large">Recepcion</span><br>
        <span>Jardein versalles</span>
        <span>8:00 PM</span>
      </li>

    </ul>
  </div>
  <hr>






<!-- END Introduction Menu -->
</div>

<!-- END GRID -->
</div><br>

<!-- END w3-content -->
</div>

<!-- Add Google Maps -->
<script>
function myMap()
{
  myCenter=new google.maps.LatLng(41.878114, -87.629798);
  var mapOptions= {
    center:myCenter,
    zoom:12, scrollwheel: false, draggable: false,
    mapTypeId:google.maps.MapTypeId.ROADMAP
  };
  var map=new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById("googleMap"),mapOptions);

  var marker = new google.maps.Marker({
    position: myCenter,
  });
  marker.setMap(map);
}
</script>
<script src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyBWavkAJEWPBMOys2-RYKOGDPtBj1EhOJc&callback=myMap"></script>



</body>
</html>
